structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 283. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 211, sec. 3.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Requirements of KRS 186.275 and 186.280 to be additional to other motor vehicle registration requirements.
